With the support of the Mastercard Foundation, the Belgian Government (the Directorate-General for Development Cooperation-DGD), and VVOB - education for development, 3,000 laptops were delivered to 30 districts in Rwanda. This initiative will help establish an enabling environment for online continuous professional development (CPD) for teachers and school leaders, which is also part of theÂ Mastercard Foundation's Leaders in Teaching initiative. Learn more. Find out more about Mastercard Foundation in Africa.